==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quinque-
<hw>Quin"que-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L. <ets>quinque</ets> five. See
<er>Five</er>.]</ety> <def>A combining form meaning <xex>five</xex>,
<xex>five times</xex>, <xex>fivefold</xex>; <as>as, <ex>quinque</ex>fid,
five-cleft; <ex>quinque</ex>dentate, five-toothed.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

